## Design System

### Color Palette
| Context | Color | Hex | Usage |
|---------|-------|-----|-------|
| Primary | Blue | #4A90E2 | Links, buttons, highlights |
| Accent | Green | #7ED321 | Success, positive actions |
| Warning | Orange | #F5A623 | Warnings, alerts |
| Danger | Red | #E63946 | Errors, destructive actions |
| Neutral Light | Light Gray | #F5F7FA | Backgrounds, dividers |
| Neutral Dark | Dark Gray | #1C1F26 | Text, borders |

### Typography
| Element | Font | Weight | Size | Line-Height |
|---------|------|--------|------|------------|
| Headings | Inter | 700 | 2.5rem (H1) | 1.2 |
| Body | Inter | 400 | 1rem | 1.6 |
| Code | Fira Code | 400 | 0.875rem | 1.4 |
| Small | Inter | 400 | 0.875rem | 1.5 |

### Spacing (Tailwind)
- 4px (0.25rem), 8px (0.5rem), 16px (1rem), 24px (1.5rem), 32px (2rem)

### Breakpoints (Responsive)
- Mobile: 0-767px (`sm`)
- Tablet: 768-1199px (`md`, `lg`)
- Desktop: 1200px+ (`xl`, `2xl`)

## Accessibility Standards (WCAG 2.1 AA)

✅ **Color Contrast**: 4.5:1 for text, 3:1 for graphics
✅ **Keyboard Navigation**: Tab through all interactive elements
✅ **Semantic HTML**: `<header>`, `<nav>`, `<main>`, `<footer>`, proper heading hierarchy
✅ **ARIA Labels**: `aria-label`, `aria-describedby` for icons/buttons
✅ **Focus Indicators**: Clear, visible focus outlines
✅ **Alt Text**: All images have descriptive alt text
✅ **Form Labels**: All inputs have associated labels

